Helix::Driver::Template::HTML, version 0.01
===========================================

The Helix::Driver::Template::HTML is a template driver for I<Helix Framework>.
It is based on famous HTML::Template package, that provides a lot of tasty 
functions for separating code and markup.

INSTALLATION

To install the driver type the following:

    perl Makefile.PL
    make
    make test
    make install

DEPENDENCIES

To use this driver you must have the following packages installed:

    HTML::Template
    Helix

